  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a study to investigate the incidence of Obstructive Sleep Apnoea in Patient
      undergoing open heart Surgery . This will include enrolment of 400 patient undergoing open
      heart surgery .
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
